    <title>Hello World</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2022/01/07/hello-world/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2022/01/07/hello-world/</id>
    <published>2022-01-07T02:35:39.650Z</published>
    <updated>2022-01-11T05:13:21.459Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到 <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! 本文将记录Hexo+Markdown的学习手册！</p><hr><blockquote><h1 id="Hexo手册"><a href="#Hexo手册" class="headerlink" title="Hexo手册"></a>Hexo手册</h1></blockquote><h2 id="创建一个新的文章"><a href="#创建一个新的文章" class="headerlink" title="创建一个新的文章"></a>创建一个新的文章</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;XXX&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="创建一个新的页面"><a href="#创建一个新的页面" class="headerlink" title="创建一个新的页面"></a>创建一个新的页面</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page XXX</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="本地调试服务"><a href="#本地调试服务" class="headerlink" title="本地调试服务"></a>本地调试服务</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="生成静态文件"><a href="#生成静态文件" class="headerlink" title="生成静态文件"></a>生成静态文件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="清理页面缓冲"><a href="#清理页面缓冲" class="headerlink" title="清理页面缓冲"></a>清理页面缓冲</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="部署到远程站点"><a href="#部署到远程站点" class="headerlink" title="部署到远程站点"></a>部署到远程站点</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><h1 id="Markdown手册"><a href="#Markdown手册" class="headerlink" title="Markdown手册"></a>Markdown手册</h1></blockquote><h2 id="标题（Heading）"><a href="#标题（Heading）" class="headerlink" title="标题（Heading）"></a>标题（Heading）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># H1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## H2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### H3</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="H1"><a href="#H1" class="headerlink" title="H1"></a>H1</h1><h2 id="H2"><a href="#H2" class="headerlink" title="H2"></a>H2</h2><h3 id="H3"><a href="#H3" class="headerlink" title="H3"></a>H3</h3><h2 id="加重语气（Emphasis）"><a href="#加重语气（Emphasis）" class="headerlink" title="加重语气（Emphasis）"></a>加重语气（Emphasis）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Emphasis, aka italics, with <span class="emphasis">*asterisks*</span> or <span class="emphasis">_underscores_</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Strong emphasis, aka bold, with <span class="strong">**asterisks**</span> or <span class="strong">__underscores__</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Strikethrough uses two tildes. ~~Scratch this.~~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Emphasis, aka italics, with <em>asterisks</em> or <em>underscores</em>. （斜体）</p><p>Strong emphasis, aka bold, with <strong>asterisks</strong> or <strong>underscores</strong>. （粗体）</p><p>Strikethrough uses two tildes. <del>Scratch this.</del> （删除线）</p><h2 id="列表（Lists）"><a href="#列表（Lists）" class="headerlink" title="列表（Lists）"></a>列表（Lists）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 有序列表（First item）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 有序列表（Second item）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">*</span> 无序列表（First item）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 无序列表（Second item）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 无序列表（Third item）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>❌ 切记无序列表不能混合使用，只能使用一种</p><ol><li>有序列表（First item）</li><li>有序列表（Second item）</li></ol><ul><li>无序列表（First item）</li></ul><h2 id="链接（links）"><a href="#链接（links）" class="headerlink" title="链接（links）"></a>链接（links）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">这是一个内联风格的链接</span>](<span class="link">https://www.google.com</span>)</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">这是一个带标题内联风格的链接</span>](<span class="link">https://www.google.com &quot;Google&#x27;s Homepage&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">鼠标悬停查看标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://www.google.com/">这是一个内联风格的链接</a><br><a href="https://www.google.com/" title="Google&#39;s Homepage">这是一个带标题内联风格的链接</a><br>鼠标悬停查看标题</p><h2 id="图像（Images）"><a href="#图像（Images）" class="headerlink" title="图像（Images）"></a>图像（Images）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">内联样式:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt text</span>](<span class="link">https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png &quot;Logo Title Text 1&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">外链样式:</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt text</span>][<span class="symbol">logo</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">logo</span>]: <span class="link">https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png &quot;Logo Title Text 2&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>内联样式:</p><p><img src="https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png" alt="alt text" title="Logo Title Text 1"></p><p>外链样式:<br><img src="https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png" alt="alt text" title="Logo Title Text 2"></p><h2 id="区块引用（Blockquotes）"><a href="#区块引用（Blockquotes）" class="headerlink" title="区块引用（Blockquotes）"></a>区块引用（Blockquotes）</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 这是一个区块引用演示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; #### 当然你可以与前面学过的混合使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; - 无序列表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 1. 有序列表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt;  <span class="emphasis">*这是一个斜体*</span> 当然也可以 <span class="strong">**这是一个粗体**</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这是一个区块引用演示</p><h4 id="当然你可以与前面学过的混合使用"><a href="#当然你可以与前面学过的混合使用" class="headerlink" title="当然你可以与前面学过的混合使用"></a>当然你可以与前面学过的混合使用</h4><ul><li>无序列表</li></ul><ol><li>有序列表</li></ol><p> <em>这是一个斜体</em> 当然也可以 <strong>这是一个粗体</strong></p></blockquote><h2 id="（水平标尺）Horizontal-Rule"><a href="#（水平标尺）Horizontal-Rule" class="headerlink" title="（水平标尺）Horizontal Rule"></a>（水平标尺）Horizontal Rule</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是三种样式且功能相同</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong">可以任选其一进行使用</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"><span class="strong">____</span><span class="strong">____</span><span class="strong">____</span><span class="strong">____</span>_</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"><span class="strong"></span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>这是三种样式且功能相同</p><hr><p>可以任选其一进行使用</p><hr><h2 id="（表情样式）Expression"><a href="#（表情样式）Expression" class="headerlink" title="（表情样式）Expression"></a>（表情样式）Expression</h2><p>😊  😃  ☺️<br>💙  💜  ❤️<br>这么炫酷的表情怎么写入文章呢?<br>那当然是<kbd>ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>c</kbd>+<kbd>v</kbd><br>没错它可以直接写入markdown当中，详见作者的<a href="https://gist.github.com/rxaviers/7360908">GitHub</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
